    public class FixedFeatureGramClassifier<WINDATA,FDATA>
extends AbstractFixedFeatureExtractingClassifier<WINDATA,FDATA>
implements IFixedClassifier<WINDATA>
    Extends the super class to implement its methods using an instance of IFixedFeatureGramClassifier. This class uses the super class to extract the features and the IFixedFeatureGramClassifier to actually do the classification.
